What you need to know:

Ms Ogodo and Mr Akungo fought over the Speaker’s chair which the latter was dragging away before she sustained a broken arm.The ensuing melee also saw Ms Grace Oyamo, another nominated MCA, wrestled to the ground by God Jope MCA Mr Leo Lot.The pro-Obado MCAs led by Mr Akungo had walked into the plenary and disrupted the session chaired by Mr Omamba.